Our group project was on Convolutional Neural Networks. We used the data sets from moths and butterflies from Kaggle and did it on google
colab. When running the model and code, we had to make sure to have the images saved and linked to the google colab folder. 
This made it easier to run. Additionally, the training had to use high computational power making it very expensive.

In the repository we have attached the code for both of the models as well as the pdf of the model showing results.
The presentation of the project is also found in the repository.
